      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/h2o-to-offer-millions-to-irate-clients-in-bid-to-dodge-a-uk-fine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[H2O Asset Management 正在寻求通过向自 2020 年以来一直被阻止获得当时价值约 16 亿欧元（17 亿美元）投资的愤怒客户提供补偿来避免英国罚款。]]></description>
